  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nsee figma:\r\n- https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=1023%3A298171\r\n- https://www.figma.com/file/idUoxN7OIW2Jpp3PMJ1Rl8/%E2%9A%99%EF%B8%8F-Settings-%7C-Desktop?node-id=1592%3A128606\r\n\r\nSupport syncing from desktop, if mobile does not support this yet, then it should be done in a different task.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"868\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-05-30 at 7 08 40 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/171066806-6e03d8e8-6f1c-4925-aaef-3e71258b3c89.png\">\r\n\r\ngoals:\r\n- [ ] write feature spec describing syncing in https://github.com/status-im/feature-specs\r\n- [ ] update settings syncing screen\r\n- [ ] Support syncing with another desktop app\r\n\r\nnote:\r\n- status-go apis for this should already exist, but it's possible some might need to be implemented\r\n- keycard syncing is out of scope\r\n- [PR#5756](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/5756) might be relevant if scanning QR codes is required",
